Experiment and have fun as Agent 47. Become the best assassin in the world! Travel to the most exotic countries of the world, eliminate targets using any weapon from a katana and a sniper rifle to golf ball bombs and expired sauce. 

   HITMAN™ Game of the Year Edition includes:  

  - all locations and missions from HITMAN season 1;
  - bonus campaign "Patient Zero";
  - 3 thematic contracts for escalation;
  - 3 suits;
  - 3 types of weapons.

Unique Builds for Every Run
 Choose from a variety of upgrades in this action roguelike to create unique builds for each of your characters on each run. Will you be a Chef, making desserts or frying your enemies? A Seamstress, stitching your enemies together or smashing them with your yarn balls? Will you choose wood or marble for your statues? Find your own way to SURVIVE! 

  Choose Your Master
 Choose from a variety of masters and artisans, each with their own unique set of skills and mechanics, to create a different gaming experience. Cooking enemies, stitching them together, or creating statues that will crush your enemies - there is always a clever way to protect your home!  

 Improve your village and become more powerful
 Collect materials from enemies and use them to improve your village, unlocking new characters and additional power-ups, thereby increasing your power even more. 

  Choose how you play
 Switch abilities between manual and automatic modes individually! Find what works best in each mode, adapting it to your play style! All manual? All abilities on automatic? Or a combination of both? The choice is yours!  

 Features:
 -Fight in a variety of biomes with their own special challenges, which are added in updates;
 -A wide selection of craftsmen and artisans, which become more with updates;
 -Discover different skill trees for each character, in total there are more than 100 skills available;
 -Quick game sessions for busy gamers;
 -The food system allows you to diversify the game even more;
 -Blacksmithing and weaving allow you to acquire more than 80 new passive skills, allowing you to adapt the playstyle of each character.

Here’s the text with line breaks as requested:  Darkham, with its humped roofs and garrets, dark alleys, and a past shrouded in mystery... This city has never been particularly hospitable, but now! The city is filled with crazy sects, and disturbing whispers once again carry the name of the greatest Book of Evil, the Necronomicon.

 Detective Don A.R. Hetip is searching for this mysterious and sinister book, but unsuspecting librarian Buzz Kerwan stumbles upon it and accidentally turns his cat Kitty into a hideous abomination. Humanization?! Yeah, that's as low as it gets.

 Gibbous is a cosmic horror comedy adventure. A classic-inspired adventure with gorgeous, high-quality art, detailed traditional animation, and a long-running storyline. As it unfolds, the three main characters will travel around the world and encounter monsters, both cosmic and man-made, as well as voodoo and That Which Should Not Be. From Lovecraft Country to Transylvania, embark on a journey to finally shut up this cynical cat.

 Peculiarities:

 • Over 60 hand-drawn, highly detailed locations inspired by Transylvanian architecture and nature;

 • Traditional smooth 2D animation in Disney style;

 • Two main characters and a talking cat... Okay, three. Three main characters;

 • Over 70 fully voiced, amazing characters;

 • Cameo guest star Doug Cockle, voice of the Witcher;

 • The game boasts the most authentic Transylvanian accent in the history of gaming and media in general;

 • Over 4 hours of atmospheric, original soundtrack with live instruments;

 • A long cinematic story spanning continents and beyond;

 • Humor at every turn, while the main plot is dark;

 • Dynamic lighting, real-time reflections, advanced weather system;

 • Built-in hint system in case you get stuck;

 • Fully animated cartoon title cards that mark important plot points;

 • Over 12,000 voiced lines of dialogue;

 • Voiced reactions to any, even the craziest combinations that come into your head;

 • Made with love right next to the birthplace of Count Dracula;

 • No witticisms or jibes directed at the Great Old Ones, may their Dark Names be glorified;

 • Did we mention the talking cat?

Metro: Last Light Redux is the definitive, most complete version of the classic Metro: Last Light game, updated with the latest, most advanced version of the 4A Engine graphics core for the latest generation of gaming systems. 

  Players new to the series will get one of the best story-driven shooters of all time – an epic adventure that combines gripping survival horror, exploration, tactical combat and stealth. This edition also includes all previously released downloadable content, which adds an additional 10 hours of single-player gameplay. 

  Fans of the game in its original form will notice that the mechanics have been improved and new features have appeared - for example, the ability to check the time and ammunition at any time, and the battles and figures of the game characters have been re-animated. 

  Those who were drawn to the famous Metro 2033 prequel with its focus on horror and survival will be able to play in a new way, as there are now two ways to play – “Survival” and “Spartan”. In the first way, Last Light turns from a game with an emphasis on combat and stealth actions into a quiet but tense fight for survival. 

  The incomparable Ranger Mode makes the game even more exciting and challenging, so Metro: Last Light Redux will provide you with hours of entertainment at a great price. 

  Game Features: 
  Descend into the depths of the Moscow metro - one of the most atmospheric worlds in the history of gaming will appear before you with stunning updated next-gen graphics and a frame rate of 60FPS; 
 Survive the horrors of the Russian apocalypse - put on a gas mask, fight off terrifying mutants and hostile people, survive in a deadly environment; 
 Updated and remastered for the latest consoles, the game includes all previously released DLC packs, new modes and features, and numerous gameplay improvements. This is the definitive version of the successful series that will appeal to long-time fans and newcomers alike; 
 Two unique gameplay styles: Spartan and Survival – fight for survival in the Survival Horror style or use the combat skills of a Ranger; 
 The legendary Ranger Mode is back – will you dare to play the super-hard Ranger Mode? With no GUI, deadly enemies on every corner and a constant shortage of ammo, you are guaranteed a completely immersive experience. 

 OS: OS X 10.9.5 Mavericks or newer

mac_softwares.description:
App Cleaner & Uninstaller helps you save space on your Mac when uninstalling apps. It's no secret that simply dragging an app icon to the Trash to uninstall it doesn't remove the service files associated with that app.



App Cleaner & Uninstaller allows you to:



Remove applications completely;

Delete all types of service files;

Delete the remaining files of applications that were previously deleted to the Recycle Bin;

Remove or disable extension files;

Customize which apps load when you start your Mac.
